steps.instruction:
Made by Andy Baraghani and can be found [here](https://www.bonappetit.com/recipe/herby-garlic-confit)

### Prep
- Separate the garlic cloves and unpeel then

### Steps
1. Preheat oven to 250
2. Place garlic, herbs, and oil in an 8x8" baking dish or a small saucepan
3. Cover with foil and bake until garlic is tender, 6075 minutes.
    - (Youll have to pop one out of its skin to test it; it should be soft and jammy.) 
4. Let cool.

#### Tips
- Garlic confit can be made 2 weeks ahead. Transfer to an airtight container and chill. Reheat over low heat before using.
